            <p>The current functionality is such that any word or path delimiter found in Zend_Controller_Dispatcher_Standard will be substituted with a dash ('-') by the ViewRenderer. Thus, the URI /two-words/index will call TwoWordsController::indexAction() and render the view script two-words/index.phtml. This is to be internally consistent with how the controller and action names are passed via the request object.</p>

